70,"category":1583,"category_id":89,"featured":16,"id":1584,"is_redirect":16,"lead":1585,"locked":16,"origin_domain":33,"parent_domain":57,"parent_id":57,"premium":16,"priority":392,"published":66,"published_at":1586,"recommended":16,"redirect_url":57,"short_title":1587,"slug":1588,"sponsored":42,"sub_title":1589,"title":1590,"uid":1584,"updated_at":1591,"stats":1592,"is_photostory":16,"is_advertisement":16,"is_pool":16,"show_quiz_cover":42,"view_type":1018},34448,{"id":1571,"name":60,"url":1572,"thumbnail":60,"created_at":1573,"tags":60,"author":1574,"type":999,"filename":1575,"description":1576,"750x750px":1577,"160x90px":1578,"365x225px":1579,"100x100px":1580,"760xautopx":1581,"1200x675px":1582},51461,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/347e589a-a379-4e76-8170-2dba15b1d1d8","2026-03-09 10:30:47","Komenda Powiatowa Policji w Kole","347e589a-a379-4e76-8170-2dba15b1d1d8","Pozornie „niewinna zabawa” mogła zakończyć się tragedią. 23-letni mieszkaniec powiatu kolskiego został nocą wywieziony do lasu i pozostawiony tam bez odzieży, przy temperaturze oscylującej wokół zera.","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/fe82dc92-124b-4157-8708-818b6006911a","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/c50c7800-bae5-41f2-b73d-5ef7d8adde53","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/b0e50f29-ca0c-4489-b5b1-8d72fc0e1eed","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/3947765a-d2fc-45ac-a08c-b1288f212540","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/a4b52ff4-e277-4591-a348-eb27d2a6f4ae","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/01a24e4c-4772-458b-bff8-00760360e86f",[86],"CHFXG4ddzV75EfJbdUiB","W zamyśle miał być to zabawny „challenge”, a o mało nie doszło do tragedii. Znajomi wywieź