zwielkopolski24/articles/image/e3b0141d-20bf-4892-b15d-0bf341c63718","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/0c99ff6a-0ae5-4fd1-ba4d-1493fa16ea4d","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/bb39db21-d6b4-4fb1-a444-78da19b84ca3","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/cfd2b365-ec65-4643-a80e-96e64860af3f","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/350950f7-738d-443a-aa51-2af9eea422d2","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/837cbdd8-0110-4ac3-85b4-bb274567e88b",[86],"w7NUFEDANVXXu6kvF4LN","Rosnący w sercu poznańskiej Wildy dąb szypułkowy \"Krzysztof\" znalazł się w gronie 16. finalistów konkursu \"Drzewo Roku\". Już w czerwcu będzie potrzebował naszych głosów, by móc reprezentować Polskę na arenie europejskiej.","2026-03-08 13:00:00","Ma 300 lat i przetrwał dwie wojny","ma-300-lat-i-przetrwal-dwie-wojny-dab-krzysztof-z-poznanskiej-wildy-powalczy-o-prestizowy-tytul","Dąb \"Krzysztof\" z poznańskiej Wildy powalczy o prestiżowy tytuł","Ma 300 lat i przetrwał dwie wojny. Dąb \"Krzysztof\" z poznańskiej Wildy powalczy o prestiżowy tytuł","2026-03-07 21:31:05",{"comments":16},{"aid":1644,"attachments":1645,"category":1657,"category_id":62,"featured":16,"id":1658,"is_redirect":16,"lead":1659,"locked":16,"origin_domain":33,"parent_domain":57,"parent_id":57,"premium":16,"priority":392,"published":66,"published_at":1660,"recommended":16,"redirect_url":57,"short_title":1661,"slug":1662,"sponsored":42,"sub_title":1663,"title":1664,"uid":1658,"updated_at":1665,"stats":1666,"is_photostory":16,"is_advertisement":16,"is_pool":16,"show_quiz_cover":42,"view_type":1018},34391,{"id":1646,"name":60,"url":1647,"thumbnail":60,"created_at":1648,"tags":60,"author":1649,"type":999,"filename":1650,"description":60,"750x750px":1651,"160x90px":1652,"365x225px":1653,"100x100px