icyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/2d6fc198-fa75-44da-92d7-93f7a7775a28","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/8f1e7f71-3b22-4a28-bd8c-5fee724f3d61","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkopolski24/articles/image/ccd9eab2-23f0-4cd7-b721-ffb6350ec7bb",[110],"ztGX3CFHAOBeFQime7ha","Zaledwie trzy godziny drogi od Poznania rozciąga się jeden z najpiękniejszych parków Europy - Park Mużakowski. To wyjątkowe miejsce, wpisane na listę światowego dziedzictwa UNESCO, zachwyca harmonijnym połączeniem natury i historii. Bajkowy zamek, romantyczne mosty, urokliwe trasy rowerowe, malownicze pejzaże - te widoki zapadają w pamięć o każdej porze roku.","2026-02-22 16:00:00","Zamek, mosty i 700 ha natury","zamek-i-park-jak-z-bajki-perla-z-listy-unesco-rzut-beretem-od-poznania","Park Mużakowski to perła UNESCO","Zamek, mosty i 700 hektarów natury. Park Mużakowski to perła UNESCO","2026-02-22 13:53:19",{"comments":16},{"module":1748,"size":141},[1749],{"name":986,"config":1750,"type":990,"articles":1751},{"mobile":12,"mobile_full":57,"mobile_intern":57,"type":1146,"query":1719,"limit":66,"skip":66,"category":1719},[1752],{"aid":1753,"attachments":1754,"category":1766,"category_id":114,"featured":16,"id":1767,"is_redirect":16,"lead":1768,"locked":16,"origin_domain":33,"parent_domain":57,"parent_id":57,"premium":16,"priority":392,"published":66,"published_at":1769,"recommended":16,"redirect_url":57,"short_title":1770,"slug":1771,"sponsored":42,"sub_title":1772,"title":1773,"uid":1767,"updated_at":1774,"stats":1775,"is_photostory":16,"is_advertisement":16,"is_pool":16,"show_quiz_cover":42,"view_type":1018},33929,{"id":1755,"name":60,"url":1756,"thumbnail":60,"created_at":1757,"tags":60,"author":1758,"type":999,"filename":1759,"description":60,"750x750px":1760,"160x90px":1761,"365x225px":1762,"100x100px":1763,"760xautopx":1764,"1200x675px":1765},50870,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/zwielkop